entries.femaleVariant: <kiroshi l="creo" o="Yo pran mesye pandan yo tap okipe net la." t="They got him while they were mapping de net." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Tonnè. Mesye te konn toujou fè atansyon." t="Fuck. He was always so careful." b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Ou konnen pou kisa mesye te kon fè atansyon?" t="And you know why he was careful?" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Paske mesye te panse li te fèb, li te initil!" t="Because he thought he was weak! That he was useless!" b="" a=""/>
<kiroshi l="creo" o="Pèsonn moun pa te janm fòse mesye nan anyen." t="No one forced him into anything." b="" a=""/>
